<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="clear-the-air">clear the air</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>缓解紧张状态：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Our conversation was filled with arguments; and efforts to clear the air seemed to deepen our misunderstanding.
我们的谈话充满了争论；为缓解紧张气氛所作出的努力似乎都在加深误会。</p><footer>2010 全国改</footer></div></div>